data.text:
Jandaq, Isfahan, Iran

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 34.041668, 54.415558.

Jandaq is a small town in the province of Isfahan, located in central Iran. It is located near Highway 81 and it is a county seat for Khur and Biabanak county. The population of the town is close to 4,000 people, and the town is very well provided with most of the social services common for the developed world.
